Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.26,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{My new song, "A Farewell to Yukichi."}Bài hát mới "Tạm biệt ngài Yukichi".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.58,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry!}Chị xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I hate it too, okay?}Chị cũng đau lòng lắm.
