Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.24,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:20.32,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Maybe we could work at\Na beach house or something!}Làm việc ở bãi biển thì sao?
