Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.68,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{When I read Bocchi's lyrics, \Nit just came to me.}Khi đọc lời của Bocchi thì nhạc tự nhiên phát ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.20,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That's awesome!}Tuyệt ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{All the hard work paid off!}Chúng ta đã được đền đáp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.92,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{That's my girl. There, there.}Em giỏi lắm, ngoan ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:13.32,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai! I'm working hard, too!}E-Em cũng cố gắng nữa nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.32,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Watch me!}Xem em đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.32,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I've gotten so good at guitar!}Em có thể chơi ghita rồi nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:18.50,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Amazing.}Tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.03,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Amazing?!}Tuyệt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.44,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Please give me chin rubs, too!}Vậy xoa đầu em đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.56,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{There, there.}Rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.29,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{My dream might just come true.}Giấc mơ của chị thành hiện thực rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:28.54,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.14,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'll ask Sis to let us hold \Nour concert here next month!}Chị sẽ nhờ chị mình mở buổi diễn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.42,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You hadn't asked her yet?}Chị vẫn chưa hỏi chị ấy hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.16,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{No worries!}Không sao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.27,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She let us in right away last time!}Lần trước hỏi cái cho luôn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.75,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Right, Sis?}Nhỉ chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.76,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{I'm not putting you on.}Không nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.14,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:45.85,Default,Hitori/Kita,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.46,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.83,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.21,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.96,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.60,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked being soaked by the rain,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.97,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{because my face looked better clouded over}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.61,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be afraid of the storm}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.44,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{while waiting for the sky to burst}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:32.40,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum through the light's distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.82,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to make thunder roar}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:42.62,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum beyond the pain}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.75,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:52.81,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum in a harmonizing quartet}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.80,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to cause a revolution}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:02.81,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum in a lamenting forte}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:07.56,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild}
