Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.98,BText,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs17\b0\pos(437,107)}{Potential August Bands\N\N• Macaroni Pencil\N\N• Yukiguni with Tunnel}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:21.92,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But why? We just finished our original song.}Tại sao? Bọn em vừa hoàn thành bài hát gốc mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.17,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Why should I care about that?}Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-This feels super awkward...}C-Cảm giác không ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.80,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We can even pay our quota \Nif we don't bring in customers!}Bọn em sẽ trả phần vé của khán giả nếu không ai xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.50,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{It's not about the money.}Không phải về tiền bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.21,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{It's about your skill.}Về kĩ năng cơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.04,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But you let us play last time.}Nhưng lần trước chị cho mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.44,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{I made an exception so you \Ncould make a memory.}Cái đó chỉ để tạo kỉ niệm đẹp cho em thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.25,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{"Make a memory"?}Tạo kỉ niệm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:45.30,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Normally, I'd make you play first to apply.}Bình thường phải chơi trước để đăng kí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.68,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{You know that, right?}Em biết mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.20,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but...}Vâng nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:52.58,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but I can't have a repeat \Nof that awful May performance.}Xin lỗi, chị không muốn lặp lại màn trình diễn tệ hại đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.88,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Can't have a repeat...}Không muốn lặp lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.95,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You mean we...}Tức là bọn em...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.57,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Just stick with it as a hobby or something.}Chỉ hoạt động như một nhóm chung sở thích?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.28,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{You got more to say?}Còn vấn đề gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.91,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You can't even sleep without \Nstuffed animals to cuddle!}Chị thậm chí còn ôm gấu bông ngủ mà đòi lên giọng!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.80,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Ijichi-senpai!}C-Chị Ijichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.71,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{That was a weird parting shot.}Cái câu đáp lại vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.21,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Would the stuffed animals in question}Những con thú bông đó
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.17,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{be this beat-up panda and rabbit?}có phải là thỏ và gấu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.17,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{That's cute.}Dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.52,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Delete that image! Immediately!}Xoá ngay lập tức!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.45,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{What are you doing? We have to go after her!}Phải đuổi theo chị ấy thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.68,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Don't act like it's too much trouble!}Đừng làm vẻ mặt phiền phức đó chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.97,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You too, Gotoh-san!}Cả cậu nữa Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.42,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Let's go!}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.64,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}À ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.72,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Wait, Bocchi-chan.}Khoan đã Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?}V-Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What, what, what?}Gì vậy, gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What, what, what?!}Gì vậy gì vậy gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.66,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It's so obvious when you're sulking.}Cậu quá dễ hiểu khi giận dỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.85,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Shut up.}Im đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.27,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Senpai, are you all right?}Chị ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.05,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Sorry to rush out like that.}Xin lỗi vì tự nhiên bỏ chạy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.12,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She didn't have to be such \Na jerk about it, you know?}Chị ấy cũng không cần nói thế chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.05,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,M-Mấy chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.86,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.55,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me...}E-Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.74,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{M-Manager... said...}C-Chị ấy... nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.29,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She said...}Chị ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.90,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, breathe first!}Bocchi, thở trước!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Here, Bocchi-chan!}Đây, Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you.}C-Cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.69,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Feel better?}Ổn lại chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.04,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:31.32,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Um... The manager told me...}Quản lý nói em...
